Sulfuras
increase damage and strenght but remove attack speed attack will burn the target for high damage can be use for swing dealing insane
damage in a large area, Volcanus will get increase bonus from this item and the only weapon he can wield

Active item use Sulfuras Swing
Swing Sulfuras dealing 150 fire damage plus 70% of the user strenght in a 500 radius in front of the caster stuning for 2 second
any enemy that die upon Sulfuras Swing will give a charge that will empower Sulfuras after getting the right amount, coldown 35 no
mana cost

Passive item use
auto-attack will burn the target for 15 fire damage plus 30% of strenght per second lasting 3 second, enemy that die during Sulfuras burn
will give a charge that will empower Sulfuras after getting the right amount and for every 100 charge increase life by 1% up to 10% and
fire damage by 2% up to 20%.

Passive item use 2
after getting 1000 charge, change the item to Sulfuras Might, increasing the bonus damage of Sulfuras Swing by 100 and Sulfuras Burn by
10 also increase the user size by 50%, increasing attack range by 130 and cleave for 40% of the damage dealt and reducing all fire type
damage by 75%

damage 60
strenght 50
attack speed lost -55
